{"tid":1991773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西正式表態支持拜登：拜登是希望同勇氣既化身","createTime":"2020-04-27T16:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T21:55:57.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a41734c6651e2989195e9306097e3fbcc11b0b","tid":1991773,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院議長波洛西，表態支持前副總統拜登，代表民主黨競逐總統寶座。<br />\n<br />\n波洛西發布短片，提到拜登過去在政府的經驗，包括協助通過奧巴馬醫保，證明他的領導才能，讚揚拜登帶來希望及勇氣，具備理性及韌性，有能力帶領國家，走出新型肺炎疫情的危機。<br />\n<br />\n波洛西是繼前總統奧巴馬及資深參議員桑德斯等人後，最新一名表態支持拜登的民主黨重量級人物。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523055-20200427.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523055-20200427.htm&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4cRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=b2e60d82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523055-20200427.htm&h=6a2ce688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523055-20200427.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;For these and other reasons, I am proud to endorse Joe Biden for President, a leader who is the personification of hope and courage, values authenticity and integrity,&quot; she said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/27/politics/nancy-pelosi-endorses-joe-biden/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F04%2F27%2Fpolitics%2Fnancy-pelosi-endorses-joe-biden%2Findex.html&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4cRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=e411dbd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2020%2F04%2F27%2Fpolitics%2Fnancy-pelosi-endorses-joe-biden%2Findex.html&h=187757d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/04/27/politics/nancy-pelosi-endorses-joe-biden/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4aiqSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4aiqSB.png&h=f71a5967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TeamPelosi/status/1254708114399600640?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTeamPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1254708114399600640%3Fs%3D20&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4cRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=a121209f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTeamPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1254708114399600640%3Fs%3D20&h=39f33a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TeamPelosi/status/1254708114399600640?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n我明白佢是民主黨高層，無得揀，點都要撐拜登既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7f757be6418cdd492b7f7c5db01216c689f616","tid":1991773,"uid":192968,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨點都要撐自己黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7269d7f2e1b3b503cce9142a587f21e1ad62a6","tid":1991773,"uid":5591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSbw5iR_sAgmmyMjXve3PXLlM4F9HkgGDFyZVqhlOUI2UX2b1R6&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSbw5iR_sAgmmyMjXve3PXLlM4F9HkgGDFyZVqhlOUI2UX2b1R6%26usqp%3DCAU&h=35474993&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77d124994e248788613280472cd363b73c90be31","tid":1991773,"uid":58552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"唔通佢撐trump咩"},{"pid":"745a0884b0e4480789b32ca1039cead6127d05a0","tid":1991773,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"支持連登先講啦"},{"pid":"6c3267171cc5741e5ec5609c8938a7e01c4cdc35","tid":1991773,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\